    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play a variety of different levels, defeat other arthropods, complete difficult trials, and collect different buggies- and weapons to use along the way. Do what you want to do in your time on Arthropod Island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay:</strong> You are an arthropod- with a weapon. Launch yourself with the recoil from your weapon to move.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lots of levels:</strong> Reach the end of each level and avoid the dangers within every level. There are multiple different areas with their own unique levels and challenges, and at the end of each area, you must face a powerful arthropod.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Frog War Trials:</strong> A strange frog offers you great rewards if you complete trials he has created. If you are able to complete these difficult trials, you will be able to obtain special buggies and weapons.</p>",
